{"type": "article", "id": 25499, "title": "从平面到立体的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-15T07:10:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 82, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070213343712NEvWAkTwjiGsl9.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">YOY 是日本的设计团队，由一个空间设计师和产品设计师组成，他们设计的灯具也爱探究物品和空间的关系。比如这个花瓶其实是一盏亚克力材料的灯，灯光的照射范围恰好是花瓶阴影的轮廓。油灯画像本身是可以“点亮”的，在图片的后面是一块磨砂透明板，导光板和 LED 灯，点亮后就像是一盏立体的灯，很微妙。<a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/works/\">这里是工作室链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133433l84hOxYoQ7HLfiFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133434zg5K96t47LVHnwPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133434EbGw2TpPR0UgkFHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133434KOfX1qhbaGeJuHcm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021334352LMCoqRFKNZnAp9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133435VWduj4IAQoLb7TxO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}